Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.91,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Manis sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.55,0:00:19.62,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Namaku Tabata Hana, 15 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.01,0:00:24.46,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku yakin aku tidak akan pernah mengalami\Ncinta pahit dan manis seperti di manga shojo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.78,0:00:26.83,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Karena aku adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.88,dialog,TV,0,0,0,,Baiklah, sekarang kita masuk\Nke segmen hiburan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.09,dialog,TV,0,0,0,,Silakan, Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.34,0:00:39.47,dialog,TV,0,0,0,,Hai! Selamat pagi! Segmen hiburan pagi ini\Nseperti biasa penuh berita menarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.31,dialog,TV,0,0,0,,Pertama, mari kita lihat topik ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.38,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yah, bahkan aku pun
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.38,0:00:48.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,tidak bisa bilang kalau aku tidak menginginkan\Nkehidupan seperti heroine di manga shojo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.89,dialog - atas,TV,0,0,0,,Adaptasi film dari manga populer\Ndengan total cetak tiga juta kopi,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.15,dialog - atas,TV,0,0,0,,"Lebih Manis dari Beri", resmi diumumkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.17,dialog - atas,Hana,0,0,0,,Pemeran utamanya adalah\Naktris muda terkenal, Sakisugi Haru,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.17,0:01:04.50,dialog - atas,Hana,0,0,0,,dan idola Aida Masagi dari Grup Mikaze,\Nkombinasi super mewah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.78,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tapi setelah hidup 15 tahun,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.78,0:01:04.51,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,aku sadar kalau paling banter\Naku cuma karakter figuran.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.51,0:01:05.86,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.67,0:01:09.35,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Belakangan ini\Nkamu berangkat sekolah pagi sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.91,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Ada apa memangnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.91,0:01:15.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya, aku masuk komite kebersihan.\NJadi ada jadwal piket pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.95,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Komite kebersihan, ya.\NBerat, tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.14,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hm, lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.71,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.33,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Bagaimana sekolah? Menyenangkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.78,0:01:27.60,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya, lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.01,0:01:29.85,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Sudah punya teman?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.85,0:01:32.61,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yah, begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.96,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.51,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Terus ada cowok yang kamu suka?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.75,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yah, begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.75,0:01:38.78,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Ada, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.05,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Pacar itu masih terlalu dini untukmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.17,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, bukan, bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.17,0:01:48.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak ada, kok.\NTidak ada orang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.18,0:01:51.34,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tenang saja, tidak usah khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.85,0:01:55.21,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Mungkin, aku seumur hidup pun\Ntidak akan punya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.21,0:01:59.31,dialog,Ibu,0,0,0,,Kok ribut banget dari pagi, Pak?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.31,0:02:03.45,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Bu, kayaknya Hana punya cowok\Nyang dia suka di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.18,dialog,Ibu,0,0,0,,Eh, masa, sih?\NApa itu benar, Hana?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.58,dialog,Ibu,0,0,0,,Dia cowok seperti apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.65,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Kok kamu senang banget, sih, Bu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.25,dialog,Ibu,0,0,0,,Tentu saja senang, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.08,dialog - atas,Hana,0,0,0,,Terima kasih makanannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.82,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku buru-buru,\Njadi mau berangkat sekarang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.24,dialog,Ayah,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar, Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.16,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, ada hal yang belum\Naku bilang ke orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.98,0:02:30.30,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yaitu, sejak masuk sekolah ini,\Naku sendirian terus.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.78,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak ada satu pun teman dari SMP,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.11,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,dan saat ada yang coba mengajak ngobrol,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.06,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,aku malah panik dan beku karena\Ntidak bisa bersosialisasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.71,0:02:43.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Akhirnya aku malah habiskan\Njam istirahat main gim di toilet.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.98,0:02:51.98,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya, kehidupan SMA-ku benar-benar kebalikan\Ndari kisah glamor di manga shojo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.76,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oke, tidak ada orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.64,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku tidak perlu\Ndatang sepagi ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.81,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak mau\Njadi pusat perhatian di kelas,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.81,0:03:18.55,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,dan aku juga tidak mau orang ketawa karena\Ncewek jelek kayak aku mainan bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.31,0:03:23.13,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dan begitulah,\Nkebiasaan ini jadi rutinitas pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.47,0:03:33.94,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Namun, ada sesuatu yang bikin nagih dari perasaan\N"cewek anggun" saat lagi mengurus bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.85,0:03:39.61,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oke, saatnya membuang bunga yang lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yang ini masih cantik.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.20,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kayak Ichigo di Lebih Manis dari Beri.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.42,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hanya bercanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.64,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh, Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.51,dialog - atas,Ueno,0,0,0,,Pagi! Pagi banget, ya, kamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.78,dialog - atas,Ueno,0,0,0,,Padahal kukira aku yang paling duluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.48,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia melihatku di momen super memalukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.58,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Oh ya, hari ini ada PR Bahasa Inggris, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.21,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku lupa total karena\Nsemalam kerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.81,0:06:01.67,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aduh, dan dia tipe cowok yang paling\Naku tidak mau melihatku seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.01,0:06:05.64,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Nomor absen 3, Ueno Yosuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.88,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ganteng dan pusat perhatian kelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.46,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tipikal cowok populer.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.11,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.70,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kalau kelakuanku tadi tersebar, habis aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.39,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Rahasia cewek jelek itu\Nbahan gosip yang sempurna!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.61,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Benar! Aku harus minta\Ndia merahasiakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.60,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tentu saja,\Nsiap kasih uang tutup mulut juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.47,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.13,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.90,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak, maksudku...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.59,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aksesori di kepalamu lucu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.11,0:06:51.51,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku malah jadi baper, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.83,0:06:55.04,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku karena terbawa suasana!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.81,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh?! Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.48,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata, tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.80,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Apa dia lagi tidak enak badan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.28,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh? Bunganya beda dari kemarin?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.98,0:07:16.99,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Selesai sudah.\NSemuanya sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.65,0:07:21.71,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Siapa suruh bergaya kayak heroine manga shojo?\NMalu banget sumpah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.78,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ini pasti bakal langsung tersebar\Nke seluruh kelas,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.96,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,dan aku bakal dapat julukan\N"si jelek penyelip bunga" atau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.19,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Andai aku punya kekuatan\Nmemutar balik waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.19,0:07:35.70,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Atau bisa menghapus ingatan orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.93,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bunyi bel itu kayak vonis hukuman mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.60,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Perutku sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.57,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Semoga saja belum ada yang tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.45,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Aku kebanyakan bikin,\Njadi kalau mau silakan makan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.04,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Ah, kalian juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, gila!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat! Ini benar-benar yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.93,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Sudah terlambat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.60,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata, kamu sudah kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.51,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.71,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kamu yakin tidak merasa sakit?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.11,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.34,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.60,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Oh ya, kami tadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.40,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.00,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Nih, buat kamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.64,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Uguisudani bawa mufin buatan sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.63,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tadi kami semua makan bareng.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.10,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ini jatahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sangat jago masak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.11,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Ueno, kamu tidak mau lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.40,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Gotanda sudah banyak banget makan,\Nbentar lagi habis.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.95,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh, serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.50,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tetsuo, itu tidak adil!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.62,0:09:16.64,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan belum ada yang tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.49,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.31,0:09:28.58,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau dibiarkan,\Nbisa ketahuan kapan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.85,0:09:33.05,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku harus cepat-cepat minta tolong\Nbiar dia janji tidak ngomong ke siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.76,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oke! Saat istirahat nanti...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.02,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Oh, itu apaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.11,dialog,Shimbashi,0,0,0,,Keren banget, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.11,0:09:50.23,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aduh, aku belum memikirkan\Nharus bilang apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.19,dialog - atas,Shimbashi,0,0,0,,Gila sih, ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.94,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, kalian lagi nonton apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.05,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Oh, Shimbashi katanya punya video lucu nih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Video lucu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.34,0:10:02.58,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku sudah lama banget\Ntidak ngobrol duluan sama siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.37,dialog - atas,Shimbashi,0,0,0,,A-Ah, iya. Ini video yang lagi viral banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.49,dialog - atas,Shimbashi,0,0,0,,U-Uguisudani, kamu mau lihat juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.11,0:10:07.54,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Pokoknya, aku harus cari momen\Nsaat Ueno sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.63,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia tidak pernah sendirian!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.00,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Bagus, Ueno!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.15,dialog,Inoue,0,0,0,,Ayo teruskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku memang selalu merasa suasana\Ndi sekitar Ueno sangat cerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.96,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia ramah, ceria, dan baik ke semua orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.66,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Seperti matahari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.46,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Keren banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.91,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bukan, bukan!\NBarusan itu cuma komentar murni,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.50,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,bukan karena aku\Nada perasaan aneh atau bagaimana.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.01,0:10:57.66,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Seseorang sepertiku seharusnya\Ntidak berbicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.14,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oh ya. Kalau tidak bisa ngomong langsung,\Naku bisa kasih surat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.81,0:11:08.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oke, aku bakal cepat-cepat selipin\Nke loker sepatunya sebelum ada yang lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo cepetan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini loker Ueno, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.74,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.24,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ternyata sudah ada yang duluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.51,0:11:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu, kasih surat cinta lewat loker\Nsepatu itu ketinggalan zaman atau tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun, tidak, kok. Ayo cepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.53,0:11:31.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.94,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Apa itu surat cinta?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hebat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.75,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya\Naku lihat surat cinta asli!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.38,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Orang populer memang beda, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.04,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tapi bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.04,0:11:46.21,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kalau suratku dimasukkan bareng itu,\Nbisa-bisa malah ganggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah balik!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lain kali saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.62,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh? Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.53,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Apa yang kamu lakukan di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.13,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.42,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kalau Ueno sendiri, kenapa ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.64,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Oh, tadi aku main bola\Nsama anak-anak kelas 4.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,O-Oh, begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.87,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia juga akrab sama anak kelas lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.31,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ya, kelas kita menang, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.29,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tapi hari ini panas banget, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.49,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Hm? Kamu bawa apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.30,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak, ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.51,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Eh? Apa ini kesempatanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.27,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Anu, Ueno...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.44,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.95,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Anu, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.51,dialog,Gotanda,0,0,0,,Yosuke. Tidak balik ke kelas?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.98,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tetsuo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.78,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku lagi ngomong sama Tabata.\NKamu balik duluan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.53,dialog,Gotanda,0,0,0,,Hm, ya sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.32,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Maaf ya, Tabata. Jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.78,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak ada apa-apa!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.98,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Maaf sudah ganggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Jangan pedulikan aku! Permisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.18,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Itu tadi apa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.05,dialog,Gotanda,0,0,0,,Hei, Yosuke. Itu siapa tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.15,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku sudah bilang itu Tabata.\NSatu kelas sama kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.21,dialog,Gotanda,0,0,0,,Apakah ada orang seperti itu di kelas kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.36,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ada, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berdiri, hormat!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.77,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Akhirnya aku tidak bisa melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hari ini rasanya sudah cukup.\NAku ke tugas piket saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.14,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bagi cewek jelek sepertiku,\Nini semua terlalu berat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.14,0:13:35.62,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku mampir ke kuil dan lempar\Nkoin persembahan pulang nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.83,dialog - atas,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.62,dialog - atas,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.40,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.71,0:13:44.36,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kamu keluar kelas buru-buru,\Nkukira sudah pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.81,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.23,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Waktu istirahat siang tadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.40,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,pembicaraan kita belum selesai, 'kan?\NGara-gara Tetsuo datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.10,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hanya...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.06,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Hanya karena itu saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.27,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.27,0:14:03.11,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Apa kamu bisa tidak memberi tahu siapa pun\Nsoal yang kamu lihat pagi ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.51,0:14:07.07,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Soal vas bunga itu dan bunganya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.48,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Jadi bunga di kelas itu\Nmemang kamu yang ganti, Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.41,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Itu bagian dari tugas komite kebersihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.69,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Dulu waktu SMP,\Ndi kelas tidak pernah ada bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.00,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Makanya aku benar-benar terharu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.54,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kamu selalu datang sepagi itu\Nbuat melakukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.55,0:14:24.31,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.64,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Hebat banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.22,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak sehebat itu, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.98,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.98,0:14:34.56,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Dari dulu aku penasaran\Nsiapa yang melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.01,0:14:36.43,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ternyata Tabata, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.15,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Apa itu berarti?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.93,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia kecewa berat karena ternyata aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.42,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku minta maaf yang sebesar-besarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.07,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh? Minta maaf kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.58,0:14:55.21,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Jadi intinya, aku cukup jaga rahasia\Nsoal Tabata yang ganti bunga di vas, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.79,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Iya. Tolong, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.09,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata pemalu juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.02,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Pemalu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.06,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ah, gawat. Waktunya kerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.61,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku harus pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.63,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya. Semangat kerjanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.68,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Meski kamu tidak minta pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.10,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,aku rasa aku tidak bakal cerita\Nke siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.81,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata. Ini rahasia kita berdua, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.41,0:15:28.99,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Itu kalimat yang terdengar seperti dari\Nmanga shojo yang bikin salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.05,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak, tenang diriku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.99,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Pasti maksudnya cuma ancaman karena\Ndia memegang kelemahanku sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.38,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Meski kamu tidak minta pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.71,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,aku rasa aku tidak bakal cerita\Nke siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.16,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata. Ini rahasia kita berdua, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.71,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,I-Itu maksudnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.68,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Maksudnya aku pegang kelemahanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.64,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Cewek jelek kayak kamu berharap apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.94,0:16:02.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ma-Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.69,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Mimpi...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.14,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Sepertinya poin kedekatannya\Nsudah cukup tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.76,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bolehkah mulai bahas topik inti?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.35,0:16:30.65,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kalau dunia nyata punya pilihan dialog\Ndan parameter kedekatan juga,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.33,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,pasti hidup akan lebih gampang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.30,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, aku harus cepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.44,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi, Tabata.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.27,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.76,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.78,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Uguisudani?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.44,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi, Tabata.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.94,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.36,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.26,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua tidak ada yang cedera, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.61,0:17:13.71,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Aduh, Ueno, kamu bikin Tabata kaget, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.20,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ah, yah...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.15,0:17:16.91,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.91,0:17:21.84,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku bakal maafkan kamu kalau kamu\Nmau bantu koreksi tugas bahasa Inggris hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.60,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh? Tapi aku jelek dalam bahasa Inggris, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.05,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.41,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Soalnya soal terjemahan\Nkali ini sangat susah,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.75,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,jadi aku ingin lihat\Njawaban orang lain juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.53,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Hm... Iya juga, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.00,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Percakapan mereka\Nmengalir begitu lancar dan alami.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.76,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Oh iya, Tabata jago bahasa Inggris, tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.91,0:17:44.16,dialog,Uguisudani,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak keberatan,\NTabata mau ikutan koreksi bareng?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.26,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Anu... tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.26,0:17:53.09,dialog,Shimbashi,0,0,0,,Hei, hei! Ajak aku juga dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini hari rapat rutin komite.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.31,0:18:01.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buat yang tergabung dalam komite,\Njangan lupa hadir, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Oke.\N- Malas banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ya, bubar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu anggota komite kebersihan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.93,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.94,dialog,Gotanda,0,0,0,,Kenapa, Yosuke?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.71,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.95,0:18:33.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga dari komite kebersihan kelas 4,\Ntapi aku mendadak ada keperluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf banget,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa tolong bantu kerjakan bagianku juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.45,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh?\NWah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.25,0:18:49.52,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Yah, mungkin mendingan kerja sendirian daripada\Ncanggung bareng orang yang belum dikenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini kita akan merawat\Nsemua taman bunga di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan kerja berpasangan antar dua kelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.13,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan di hari seperti ini justru...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Anak kelas 4 mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.21,0:19:07.81,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, sepertinya dia mendadak ada keperluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana, ya, kalau begitu barengan sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.26,0:19:15.21,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak apa-apa.\NAku bisa sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ini lumayan banyak kerjaannya, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.10,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Mu-Mungkin aku bakal telat...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.50,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Begitu, kayaknya, sih...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Njangan memaksakan diri dan semangat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.21,0:19:53.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Bukannya kamu ikut komite hari ini?\NKomite kebersihan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.79,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Komite kebersihan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini katanya merawat taman bunga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.51,0:20:02.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malas banget, jadi aku minta\Nanak kelas 3 saja yang kerjakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak marah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.98,0:20:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayaknya tidak, sih. Soalnya anaknya\Npendiam dan pakai kacamata.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.85,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tanahnya selesai juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.41,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Karena sudah makan waktu lama,\Nharus cepat-cepat tanam bunganya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.37,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Oh, ini salvia, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.93,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dulu waktu kecil aku suka isap nektarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.66,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.00,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.31,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku bantu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.84,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ini menanam bibit bunga di taman ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.61,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Eh?! Tidak usah, sungguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.58,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Eh, nanti kamu kotor, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.31,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dan ada cacing juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.46,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.10,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Anu, apakah terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.71,0:21:01.57,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku tidak suka kalau ada orang\Nyang harus kerja sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.38,0:21:08.63,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Apa mungkin Ueno berpikir\Naku ditindas karena bekerja sendirian?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.91,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak apa-apa, Ueno.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.04,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bukannya aku dipaksa mengerjakannya, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.25,0:21:19.00,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Teman kelompokku tadi katanya\Nmendadak ada urusan, jadi, itu, aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.38,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.41,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Yah, pokoknya jangan terlalu dipaksakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.41,0:21:27.03,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kalau kamu kesulitan,\Nkamu bisa mengandalkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.91,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak usah repot-repot!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.91,0:21:32.39,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin,\Nbisa-bisa aku dibenci cewek-cewek lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.21,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Jarak antar bibit sebegini cukup, tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.12,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ya, sudah pas.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.12,0:21:39.06,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.11,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ueno wangi banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.53,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Wanginya apa, ya?\NBahkan aromanya pun keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.05,0:21:59.40,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Hei, Tabata. Ini nama tanamannya apa...\Neh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.15,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tabata?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.37,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Salvia...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.00,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Apa? Tidak kedengaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.14,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, kenapa kamu kerja sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.95,0:22:19.26,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kita selesai sebelum gelap.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.78,0:22:20.85,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.85,0:22:22.69,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.60,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku cuma mempermalukan diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.05,0:22:30.30,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,I-Itu tadi... Pasti kedengaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.65,0:22:32.91,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Capek juga, jadi lapar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.87,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia dengar!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.01,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Oh iya, Tabata.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.33,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Y-Ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.34,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,A-Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.34,0:22:49.13,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku terbawa suasana dan malah ikut\Nke minimarket sepulang sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.15,0:22:51.26,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau ketemu kenalan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.71,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Dia mikirnya serius banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.71,0:22:55.94,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Pasti lapar banget dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.23,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, apa untungnya Ueno\Nbareng sama cewek kayak aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.71,0:23:01.56,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.01,0:23:04.02,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku ini pasti dianggap dompetnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.02,0:23:06.51,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku yang bayar!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.51,0:23:07.74,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tidak usah, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih telah berbelanja.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.61,0:23:13.21,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku tunggu di luar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.21,0:23:16.50,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf. Aku akan segera menyusul.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.11,0:23:21.61,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Dia sudah membantuku, sekarang aku\Nmalah membuatnya menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.61,0:23:24.96,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aduh, berapa kali\Naku menyusahkannya hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.91,0:23:35.14,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.18,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.28,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Anu, ini, sebagai ucapan\Nterima kasih hari ini, jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.29,0:23:42.91,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh?! Tidak usah repot-repot begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.91,0:23:47.73,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Ta-Tapi aku benar-benar merasa\Ntertolong waktu Ueno datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.74,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Ba-Baiklah, aku terima dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.98,0:23:53.82,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tunggu, semua ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.70,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu Ueno sukanya apa, jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.11,0:23:59.58,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku sangat menghargai perhatianmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.79,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,tapi ini sebanyak ini terlalu...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.21,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, begini saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.21,0:24:09.05,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Tidak sebanding sama yang kamu kasih,\Ntapi ini buat kamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.15,0:24:11.01,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Eh? Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.01,0:24:14.57,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Aku ingin coba juga roti\Nyang kamu pilih. Nih.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.15,0:24:18.97,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku terima. Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.41,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Aku sebenarnya suka banget karaage,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.41,0:24:24.58,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,tapi aku selalu bingung kapan waktu\Nyang pas buat pesan di kasir.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.58,0:24:25.86,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Waktu yang pas?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.03,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Enak banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.85,0:24:35.07,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, lain kali aku akan\Nmemesan karaage untuk kita berdua.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.64,0:24:41.39,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Karaage-nya nyangkut di tenggorokan!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.39,0:24:45.00,dialog,Ueno,0,0,0,,Eh?! Mau minum?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.91,0:24:50.71,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Kenapa, ya? Ueno selalu bisa datang\Nbegitu alami ke dekatku.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.05,0:25:00.21,dialog,Hana,0,0,0,,Mungkin...
